snippet.title: The Truth About Kevin Durant's Nets Experience | LeBron James & Steve Nash | MIND THE GAME
snippet.description:
Kevin Durant is back for part 2 and he’s still dropping gems. In this conversation he tells LeBron James and Steve Nash why he fell in love with the game, how he earned respect on the court at a young age, and all about the achilles injury recovery process including his advice to Jayson Tatum, Damian Lillard, and Tyrese Haliburton.

Durant and Nash, his former coach on the Brooklyn Nets, share what exactly happened during their time together and why they weren’t able to fully reach their potential. Nash also gives sage advice to his counterparts on how to transition from your playing days to the next stage of life. 

Catch up with Part 1 of KD's guest appearance: https://youtu.be/VUzP2PvXeoY

Presented by UNINTERRUPTED and Wondery.

(0:00) - Intro
(1:11) - Why Ime Udoka (Houston Rockets) and Erik Spoelstra (Miami Heat) are special coaches
(12:30) - How KD fell in love with the game
(16:35) - KD on his mother believing in him
(19:20) - Why players have to be obsessed to be great
(25:53) - KD on every contract being a re-commitment to yourself
(30:45) - Steve’s perspective on retirement
(33:52) - KD’s achilles injury advice to Jayson Tatum and Damian Lillard
(38:07) - KD and Steve share what really happened in Brooklyn
(40:03) - Why Steve was unable to reach his full potential as Nets coach

New episodes drop every Tuesday. Watch Mind The Game with LeBron James and Steve Nash for NBA interviews, analysis, highlights and more. Subscribe to our YouTube Channel, watch on Prime Video or follow Mind The Game wherever you listen to podcasts.

Follow us on social:

Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/mindthegamepod
TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@mindthegamepod
X: https://www.twitter.com/mindthegamepod
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/mindthegamepod

snippet.title: I Quit.
snippet.description:
Hey, everyone. It's me, Quackity. I just want to share with everyone that I am approaching a new phase in my life. This video has been in the works for a long time, and I hope everyone can watch in it's entirety. Nearly three years ago I inadvertently quit my main platform where I was making content, and ever since then, I’ve been working on a lot of projects which I am incredibly proud of.

Today, I want to announce my biggest project yet.

Dababel.

This is a project which I hold very dear to my heart, not because of what it is, but because of what it represents to me. I was born and raised in Mexico, my native language is Spanish - and this gave me the opportunity to experience what it was like to be in another country and not know the language. Throughout my life and my career I’ve noticed how prevalent language barriers are - no matter where you are. And Dababel is a project with the objective to help people move beyond this barrier, which has existed since the beginning of time.

This is a project for you. This is a project for everyone.

DABABEL IS FOR THE WORLD. 

Thank you for all the support, and I hope you enjoy Dababel. To my global communities, to my new viewers and old, thank you for everything!

snippet.title: Timelapse shows Texas flash floods turn dry river into deadly rapids in 20 minutes
snippet.description:
Dramatic timelapse video shows how heavy rainfall turned a dry riverbed into surging rapids in just 20 minutes, as Texas was deluged by deadly flash floods on July 4.

CCTV footage shows water begin surging into the Llano River at 17:14. Within minutes, a road crossing the river is entirely submerged, with the waterline rising significantly on both sides of the riverbank and completely covering trees and bushes.

Watch more on Independent TV: https://tinyurl.com/yc7ukx9n

snippet.title: Everything David Corenswet Did To Become Superman
snippet.description:
_Superman_ star David Corenswet breaks down everything he did to become James Gunn’s adaptation of Kal-El in the latest _DC Studios_ cinematic universe installment. The American actor talks through every step of his journey to becoming Superman: from receiving the casting call during _Twisters_ filming to gaining 45lbs before shooting.

#DavidCorenswet #Superman #DCComics

00:00 - David Corenswet on becoming Superman
00:23 - Casting: “I’m not sure I really did want to play Superman”
08:13 - Research: “You need an imperfect humanity to have heroes”
10:25 - Training: “I was aiming for about 4,500 calories per day”
11:47 - Costume: “We could get out of the suit in about four-and-a-half minutes”
13:43 - Mannerisms: “I drew directly from All-Star Superman”

GQ recommends:

snippet.title: CINICA - @PintoelProblema  FT @JohnTheis
snippet.description:
PINTO PROBLEMA X JOHN THEIS

CINICA: Gracias infinitas a todos los que han conectado con CÍNICA. Esta canción nació desde lo más real, Pinto un talento increíble que viene dándole duro desde su casa, con humildad y corazón se  une junto a John Theis y sacan esta increible cancion.
Ver cómo el público ha recibido este tema con tanto cariño nos llena de alegría y motivación pa’ seguir creando. Hoy celebramos este estreno con gratitud y con fe en que vendrán muchas más bendiciones. Que el género en Venezuela siga creciendo y que nunca falte la unión entre nosotros. ¡Dios me los bendiga a todos y gracias por ser parte de esto!

snippet.title: Jay Leno's ULTIMATE GM Restomods: Buick, Chevy, & Oldsmobile! | Jay Leno's Garage
snippet.description:

id.description:

Awalnya merupakan mobil penggerak roda depan yang inovatif, restomod Jay menampilkan sasis khusus, mesin 427 LS7 dengan turbocharger ganda, dan lebih dari 1000 tenaga kuda! ko.title: 제이 레노의 궁극의 GM 레스토모드: 뷰익, 쉐보레, 올즈모빌! | 제이 레노의 차고
ko.description:
Jay Leno's Garage 특별 에피소드에서 Jay Leno와 함께 SEMA를 위해 제작된 세 대의 놀라운 제너럴 모터스 레스토모드(Restomod)를 만나보세요. 그중에는 올해의 핫로드(Hot Rod of the Year) 수상 차량도 포함되어 있습니다! Tony Roma와 같은 GM 엔지니어들의 귀중한 도움으로 이 클래식 미국차들은 상징적인 스타일을 그대로 유지하면서 현대적인 파워풀한 차량으로 탈바꿈했습니다.

1. 1955년형 뷰익 로드마스터: Jay는 페니세이버(PennySaver)에서 구매한 1955년형 뷰익의 개인적인 역사를 이야기합니다. 572 크레이트 엔진, C5 코르벳 서스펜션, 디스크 브레이크를 장착한 이 빈티지 뷰익이 어떻게 "코르벳을 제압할 수 있을지" 직접 확인해 보세요!

2. 1932년형 보타이 듀스 로드스터:

스몰 블록 V8 엔진 출시 50주년을 기념하는 이 1932년형 쉐보레 차체는 1934년형 쉐보레 섀시에 탑재되었으며, 600마력의 427 LS7 엔진과 6단 수동 변속기를 탑재했습니다. 독특한 다이아몬드가 주입된 페인트와 현대적인 성능을 갖춘 클래식 핫로드를 제작하는 과정에서 겪은 어려움을 경험해 보세요.

3. 1966년형 올즈모빌 토로나도:

2006년 올해의 핫로드상을 수상한 이 토로나도는 진정한 경이로움을 선사합니다. 원래 획기적인 전륜구동 차량이었던 제이의 레스토모드는 맞춤형 섀시, 트윈 터보차저가 장착된 427 LS7 엔진, 그리고 1,000마력 이상의 출력을 자랑합니다! 맞춤형 휠과 견고한 50/50 무게 배분을 포함한 토로나도의 독특한 엔지니어링에 대해 알아보세요.

"방탄" 빌드, 극한의 파워를 다루는 도전, 그리고 이 미국의 전설적인 차량들을 운전하는 즐거움을 직접 경험해 보세요!

hi.title: जे लेनो के बेहतरीन जीएम रेस्टोमोड्स: ब्यूक, शेवरले और ओल्डस्मोबाइल! | जे लेनो का गैराज
hi.description:
जे लेनो के गैराज के एक विशेष एपिसोड में जे लेनो के साथ जुड़ें, क्योंकि वे SEMA के लिए बनाए गए तीन अविश्वसनीय जनरल मोटर्स रेस्टोमॉड को प्रदर्शित करते हैं, जिसमें हॉट रॉड ऑफ़ द ईयर विजेता भी शामिल है! टोनी रोमा जैसे GM इंजीनियरों की अमूल्य मदद से, इन क्लासिक अमेरिकी कारों को उनके प्रतिष्ठित स्टाइल को बनाए रखते हुए आधुनिक पावरहाउस में बदल दिया गया है।

1. 1955 ब्यूक रोडमास्टर: जे ने अपनी '55 ब्यूक के व्यक्तिगत इतिहास को याद किया, इसे पेनीसेवर से खरीदने से लेकर इसमें शादी करने तक। देखें कि इसे 572 क्रेट इंजन, C5 कॉर्वेट सस्पेंशन और डिस्क ब्रेक के साथ कैसे बदला गया, जिससे यह विंटेज ब्यूक "कॉर्वेट को पीछे छोड़ने में सक्षम है!"

2. 1932 बोटी ड्यूस रोडस्टर:

छोटे-ब्लॉक V8 की 50वीं वर्षगांठ मनाते हुए, यह '32 शेवरले बॉडी '34 शेवरले चेसिस पर स्थित है और इसमें 600 हॉर्सपावर वाला 427 LS7 इंजन और 6-स्पीड मैनुअल गियरबॉक्स है। अद्वितीय डायमंड-इन्फ्यूज्ड पेंट और आधुनिक प्रदर्शन के साथ एक क्लासिक हॉट रॉड बनाने की चुनौतियों के बारे में जानें।

3. 1966 ओल्डस्मोबाइल टोरोनाडो:

2006 में हॉट रॉड ऑफ़ द ईयर विजेता, यह टोरोनाडो एक सच्चा चमत्कार है। मूल रूप से एक ग्राउंडब्रेकिंग फ्रंट-व्हील-ड्राइव कार, जे के रेस्टोमॉड में एक कस्टम चेसिस, ट्विन टर्बोचार्जर वाला 427 LS7 इंजन और 1000 से अधिक हॉर्सपावर है! कस्टम-मेड व्हील्स और एक ठोस 50/50 वजन वितरण सहित इसकी अनूठी इंजीनियरिंग के बारे में जानें।

इन "बुलेटप्रूफ" बिल्ड्स, अत्यधिक शक्ति के साथ काम करने की चुनौतियों और इन अमेरिकी किंवदंतियों को चलाने की खुशी का अनुभव करें! जे लेनो के गैराज से कार की देखभाल और डिटेलिंग की आपूर्ति खरीदें: https://www.lenosgarage.com/shine

pl.title: NAJLEPSZE GM Restomods Jaya Leno: Buick, Chevy i Oldsmobile! | Garaż Jaya Leno
pl.description:
Dołącz do Jaya Leno w specjalnym odcinku Jay Leno's Garage, w którym zaprezentuje trzy niesamowite restomody General Motors, które zostały zbudowane na potrzeby SEMA, w tym zwycięzcę Hot Rod of the Year! Dzięki nieocenionej pomocy inżynierów GM, takich jak Tony Roma, te klasyczne amerykańskie samochody zostały przekształcone w nowoczesne potęgi, zachowując jednocześnie swój kultowy styl.

1. Buick Roadmaster z 1955 r.: Jay opowiada osobistą historię swojego Buicka z 1955 r., od kupienia go od PennySaver po zawarcie w nim związku małżeńskiego. Zobacz, jak został przekształcony dzięki silnikowi skrzyniowemu 572, zawieszeniu C5 Corvette i hamulcom tarczowym, dzięki czemu ten zabytkowy Buick jest w stanie „zmieść Corvette!”

2. Bowtie Deuce Roadster z 1932 r.:

To nadwozie Chevroleta z 1932 r., upamiętniające 50. rocznicę silnika Small-Block V8, spoczywa na podwoziu Chevroleta z 1934 r. i jest napędzane silnikiem 427 LS7 o mocy 600 koni mechanicznych i 6-biegową manualną skrzynią biegów. Odkryj wyjątkową diamentową farbę i wyzwania związane z budową klasycznego hot roda o nowoczesnej wydajności.

3. Oldsmobile Toronado z 1966 r.:

Ten Toronado, zdobywca nagrody Hot Rod of the Year w 2006 r., to prawdziwy cud techniki. Pierwotnie przełomowy samochód z napędem na przednie koła, restomod Jaya ma niestandardowe podwozie, silnik 427 LS7 z podwójnymi turbosprężarkami i ponad 1000 koni mechanicznych! Dowiedz się więcej o jego wyjątkowej inżynierii, w tym o niestandardowych kołach i solidnym rozkładzie masy 50/50.

Przeżyj te „kuloodporne” konstrukcje, wyzwania związane z pracą z ekstremalną mocą i radość z jazdy tymi amerykańskimi legendami!

ja.title: ジェイ・レノの究極のGMレストモッド：ビュイック、シボレー、オールズモビル！ | ジェイ・レノのガレージ
ja.description:
ジェイ・レノが司会を務める「ジェイ・レノのガレージ」特別エピソードでは、SEMAのために製作されたゼネラルモーターズ（GM）の素晴らしいレストモッド3台（ホットロッド・オブ・ザ・イヤー受賞車を含む）をご紹介します！トニー・ローマをはじめとするGMのエンジニアたちの惜しみない協力により、これらのクラシックアメリカンカーは、象徴的なスタイルを保ちながら、現代のパワフルなマシンへと生まれ変わりました。

1. 1955年式ビュイック・ロードマスター：ジェイが、ペニーセーバーで購入してから結婚式を挙げるまでの、愛車の55年式ビュイックの軌跡を語ります。572クレートエンジン、C5コルベットのサスペンション、そしてディスクブレーキを搭載し、このヴィンテージビュイックが「コルベットを圧倒！」するほどの車へと変貌を遂げた過程をご覧ください。

2. 1932年式 ボウタイ・デュース・ロードスター：

スモールブロックV8エンジンの50周年を記念したこの1932年式シボレー・ボディは、1934年式シボレー・シャーシに搭載され、600馬力の427 LS7エンジンと6速マニュアルギアボックスを搭載しています。ダイヤモンドを散りばめた独特の塗装と、クラシックなホットロッドに現代的なパフォーマンスを融合させたマシンを製作する難しさをご覧ください。

3. 1966年式 オールズモビル・トロネード：

2006年のホットロッド・オブ・ザ・イヤーを受賞したこのトロネードは、まさに驚異の逸品です。画期的な前輪駆動車だったジェイのレストモッドは、カスタムシャーシ、ツインターボチャージャー付き427 LS7エンジン、そして1000馬力を超えるパワーを誇ります。カスタムメイドのホイールや堅牢​​な50/50重量配分など、独自のエンジニアリングについて学びましょう。

これらの「防弾」ビルド、極限のパワーを扱う難しさ、そしてこれらのアメリカの伝説を運転する喜びを体験してください！

fr-FR.title: Les restomods GM ultimes de Jay Leno : Buick, Chevrolet et Oldsmobile ! | Le garage de Jay Leno
fr-FR.description:
Rejoignez Jay Leno dans un épisode spécial de Jay Leno's Garage où il présente trois incroyables restomods General Motors construits pour le SEMA, dont un Hot Rod de l'année ! Grâce à l'aide précieuse d'ingénieurs GM comme Tony Roma, ces voitures américaines classiques ont été transformées en véritables bolides modernes tout en conservant leur style emblématique.

1. La Buick Roadmaster de 1955 : Jay raconte l'histoire personnelle de sa Buick de 1955, de son achat au PennySaver à son mariage. Découvrez comment elle a été transformée avec un moteur 572, une suspension Corvette C5 et des freins à disque, permettant à cette Buick vintage de « surclasser une Corvette ! » 2. Le Bowtie Deuce Roadster de 1932 :

Célébrant le 50e anniversaire du V8 compact, cette carrosserie Chevrolet de 1932 repose sur un châssis Chevrolet de 1934 et est propulsée par un moteur 427 LS7 de 600 chevaux et une boîte manuelle à 6 rapports. Découvrez sa peinture diamantée unique et les défis de la construction d'un hot rod classique aux performances modernes.

3. L'Oldsmobile Toronado de 1966 :

Lauréate du prix du Hot Rod de l'année 2006, cette Toronado est une véritable merveille. À l'origine une voiture à traction avant révolutionnaire, la restauration de Jay comprend un châssis personnalisé, un moteur 427 LS7 à double turbocompresseur et plus de 1 000 chevaux ! Découvrez sa conception unique, notamment ses roues sur mesure et sa solide répartition du poids 50/50.

Découvrez ces véhicules à toute épreuve, les défis liés à la puissance extrême et le plaisir de conduire ces légendes américaines !

What is Roblox? ROBLOX is an online virtual playground and workshop, where kids of all ages can safely interact, create, have fun, and learn. It’s unique in that practically everything on ROBLOX is designed and constructed by members of the community. ROBLOX is designed for 13 to 18 year olds, but it is open to people of all ages. Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore ROBLOX — interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything — be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer “Capture the Flag” game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation. There is no cost for this first plot of virtual land. By participating and by building cool stuff, ROBLOX members can earn specialty badges as well as ROBLOX dollars (“Robux”). In turn, they can shop the online catalog to purchase avatar clothing and accessories as well as premium building materials, interactive components, and working mechanisms.

snippet.title: I'm taking a break my friends (After 58 years)!
snippet.description:
Well hello there, my dear friends! This video is a little different—no chef coat, no recipe, just a heart-to-heart. After 58 years in the kitchen and barely any breaks, I’ve finally decided it’s time to slow down and enjoy life beyond the sauté pan. So yes, I’m taking some time off! But don’t worry—Jack will keep things going while I soak up a little sunshine. Thank you for being part of this incredible journey. Your support means the world. I’ll be back soon, recharged and ready to cook something fabulous. In the meantime, enjoy the many recipes we’ve shared—and don’t forget your Mise-en-Place, my friends! Until next time…

snippet.title: THIS PIZZA CHALLENGE IN FLORIDA HAS ONLY BEEN BEATEN ONCE! | BeardMeatsFood
snippet.description:
In this week's episode we're at Crostini's Pizza & Cuisine in Deltona, Florida having a crack at their 28" pizza challenge...

Teams of two get just 28 minutes in which to finish a 28" pizza (with toppings of their choice...or just plain cheese if you're feeling a bit soggy) and if successful, not only is the meal ON THE HOUSE but you get a $50 gift card for your troubles too! It's been a while since I tried a team pizza challenge, so I gave my old mate @WayneAlgenio a call to help me try to secure the win!

pt-BR.title: ESTE DESAFIO DA PIZZA NA FLÓRIDA SÓ ​​FOI VENCIDO UMA VEZ! | BeardMeatsFood
pt-BR.description:
No episódio desta semana, estamos na Crostini's Pizza & Cuisine em Deltona, Flórida, participando do desafio de pizza de 71 cm...

Equipes de dois têm apenas 28 minutos para terminar uma pizza de 71 cm (com os ingredientes de sua escolha... ou apenas queijo puro, se estiver um pouco encharcado) e, se vencerem, não só a refeição é POR CONTA DA CASA, como também ganham um vale-presente de US$ 50! Fazia tempo que eu não participava de um desafio de pizza em equipe, então liguei para o meu velho amigo @WayneAlgenio para me ajudar a tentar garantir a vitória!

hi.title: फ्लोरिडा में यह पिज़्ज़ा चैलेंज सिर्फ़ एक बार ही जीता गया है! | BeardMeatsFood
hi.description:
इस सप्ताह के एपिसोड में हम फ्लोरिडा के डेल्टोना में क्रॉस्टिनी के पिज्जा और व्यंजन में हैं, जहाँ हम उनके 28" पिज्जा चैलेंज का प्रयास कर रहे हैं...

दो लोगों की टीमों को 28" पिज्जा (अपनी पसंद की टॉपिंग के साथ... या अगर आपको थोड़ा गीलापन महसूस हो रहा है तो सिर्फ़ सादा पनीर) खत्म करने के लिए सिर्फ़ 28 मिनट मिलते हैं और अगर वे सफल होते हैं, तो न सिर्फ़ भोजन मुफ़्त में मिलेगा बल्कि आपको अपनी परेशानियों के लिए $50 का उपहार कार्ड भी मिलेगा! मुझे टीम पिज्जा चैलेंज आज़माए हुए काफ़ी समय हो गया है, इसलिए मैंने अपने पुराने साथी @WayneAlgenio को कॉल किया ताकि वे मुझे जीत सुनिश्चित करने में मदद कर सकें!

snippet.title: Floods devastate Texas hill country as death toll approaches 70
snippet.description:
President Donald Trump has approved federal disaster assistance for the state of Texas to assist in recovery efforts after massive floods destroyed dozens of homes and killed nearly 70 people. The funding is available to affected individuals in Kerr County, with assistance including grants for temporary housing and home repairs, low-cost loans to cover uninsured property, and various other recovery programs. Funding will also be available to state and local governments, as well as certain nonprofits, for emergency work and the repair of critical infrastructure, as well as the repair or replacement of facilities.

snippet.title: Alex Bowman on Bubba Wallace: "I Really Thought We Had Squashed Our Beef, but Clearly We Haven't"
snippet.description:
Alex Bowman voices his thoughts on the late race contact with Bubba Wallace following the NASCAR Cup Series race at Chicago. Bowman and Wallace raced hard as the laps winded down which ended with Wallace spinning off the No. 48 team's bumper. Frontstretch's Bryan Nolen was among those who spoke to Bowman after the race.

snippet.title: I Tried an Ultra Luxury Ritz Carlton Cruise
snippet.description:
Get started with Odoo today: https://www.odoo.com/r/ksR 
I’m getting onboard one of the world’s most luxurious cruise ships, the brand new Ritz Carlton Yacht, Ilma. I’ve booked a signature suite for the next 7 days, and I’ll be showing you everything this First Class ship has to offer. From the many restaurants (including a 10 course tasting menu for $700!), the pools, floating marina and we shall even take a look at the best room onboard, the owners suite. 

For reference as usual I paid in full for this cruise, as I don’t work with the cruise lines, to the tune of over $28,000 dollars! It’s actually not my first time onboard a Ritz Carlton Yacht, having tried their previous ship Evrima a couple of years ago. There were quite a few teething issues onboard that sailing, so I’m keen to see how they’ve changed (or if they have!) with the addition of Ilma and Luminara. These new ships are larger, with even more staterooms and facilities. As always do let me know what you think down below.

id.title: Saya Mencoba Pelayaran Mewah Ritz Carlton
id.description:
Mulailah dengan Odoo hari ini: https://www.odoo.com/r/ksR 
Saya akan naik ke salah satu kapal pesiar termewah di dunia, Ritz Carlton Yacht yang baru, Ilma. Saya telah memesan suite khusus untuk 7 hari ke depan, dan saya akan menunjukkan kepada Anda semua yang ditawarkan kapal Kelas Utama ini. Dari banyak restoran (termasuk menu mencicipi 10 hidangan seharga $700!), kolam renang, marina terapung, dan kita bahkan akan melihat kamar terbaik di atas kapal, suite pemilik. 

Sebagai referensi seperti biasa, saya membayar penuh untuk pelayaran ini, karena saya tidak bekerja dengan perusahaan pelayaran, dengan jumlah lebih dari $28.000 dolar! Sebenarnya ini bukan pertama kalinya saya naik Ritz Carlton Yacht, setelah mencoba kapal mereka sebelumnya Evrima beberapa tahun yang lalu. Ada beberapa masalah awal di atas pelayaran itu, jadi saya ingin melihat bagaimana mereka telah berubah (atau apakah mereka telah berubah!) dengan penambahan Ilma dan Luminara. Kapal-kapal baru ini lebih besar, dengan lebih banyak kabin dan fasilitas. Seperti biasa, beri tahu saya pendapat Anda di bawah ini.

03:24 - Suite saya

hi.title: मैंने अल्ट्रा लग्जरी रिट्ज कार्लटन क्रूज की कोशिश की
hi.description:
आज ही Odoo के साथ शुरुआत करें: https://www.odoo.com/r/ksR
मैं दुनिया के सबसे शानदार क्रूज जहाजों में से एक, बिल्कुल नए रिट्ज कार्लटन यॉट, इल्मा पर सवार होने जा रहा हूँ। मैंने अगले 7 दिनों के लिए एक सिग्नेचर सुइट बुक किया है, और मैं आपको इस फर्स्ट क्लास जहाज की हर सुविधा दिखाऊँगा। कई रेस्तराँ (जिसमें $700 में 10 कोर्स का टेस्टिंग मेन्यू भी शामिल है!), पूल, फ़्लोटिंग मरीना और हम जहाज पर सबसे अच्छे कमरे, ओनर्स सुइट पर भी नज़र डालेंगे।

हमेशा की तरह संदर्भ के लिए मैंने इस क्रूज के लिए पूरा भुगतान किया, क्योंकि मैं क्रूज लाइनों के साथ काम नहीं करता, $28,000 से ज़्यादा की राशि! यह वास्तव में रिट्ज कार्लटन यॉट पर मेरा पहला बार सवार होना नहीं है, मैंने कुछ साल पहले उनके पिछले जहाज एवरिमा को आज़माया था। उस नौकायन में जहाज़ पर कुछ शुरुआती समस्याएँ थीं, इसलिए मैं यह देखने के लिए उत्सुक हूँ कि इल्मा और ल्यूमिनारा के जुड़ने से वे कैसे बदल गए हैं (या क्या वे बदल गए हैं!)। ये नए जहाज़ बड़े हैं, और उनमें और भी ज़्यादा स्टेटरूम और सुविधाएँ हैं। हमेशा की तरह मुझे नीचे बताएँ कि आप क्या सोचते हैं।

pl.title: Wypróbowałem rejs Ultra Luxury Ritz Carlton
pl.description:

Wsiadam na pokład jednego z najbardziej luksusowych statków wycieczkowych na świecie, zupełnie nowego jachtu Ritz Carlton Yacht, Ilma. Zarezerwowałem apartament firmowy na najbliższe 7 dni i pokażę Ci wszystko, co ten statek pierwszej klasy ma do zaoferowania. Od wielu restauracji (w tym 10-daniowego menu degustacyjnego za 700 USD!), basenów, pływającej mariny, a nawet przyjrzymy się najlepszemu pokojowi na pokładzie, apartamentowi właściciela. 

Jak zwykle zapłaciłem za ten rejs w całości, ponieważ nie współpracuję z liniami rejsowymi, w wysokości ponad 28 000 dolarów! Właściwie to nie jest mój pierwszy raz na pokładzie jachtu Ritz Carlton, ponieważ kilka lat temu wypróbowałem ich poprzedni statek Evrima. Na pokładzie tego rejsu było sporo problemów z ząbkowaniem, więc chętnie zobaczę, jak się zmieniły (lub czy się zmieniły!) po dodaniu Ilmy i Luminary. Te nowe statki są większe, mają jeszcze więcej kabin i udogodnień. Jak zawsze, dajcie mi znać poniżej, co o nich myślicie.

it.title: Ho provato una crociera ultra lusso Ritz Carlton

Salgo a bordo di una delle navi da crociera più lussuose al mondo, il nuovissimo Ritz Carlton Yacht, Ilma. Ho prenotato una suite esclusiva per i prossimi 7 giorni e vi mostrerò tutto ciò che questa nave di Prima Classe ha da offrire. Dai numerosi ristoranti (incluso un menu degustazione di 10 portate a 700 dollari!), alle piscine, al porto turistico galleggiante, e daremo persino un'occhiata alla migliore camera a bordo, la suite armatoriale.

Come al solito, ho pagato per intero questa crociera, dato che non lavoro con le compagnie di crociera, per un totale di oltre 28.000 dollari! In realtà non è la mia prima volta a bordo di un Ritz Carlton Yacht, avendo provato la loro precedente nave, l'Evrima, un paio di anni fa. Ci sono stati parecchi problemi iniziali a bordo di quella nave, quindi sono curioso di vedere come sono cambiati (o se lo sono cambiati!) con l'aggiunta di Ilma e Luminara. Queste nuove navi sono più grandi, con ancora più cabine e servizi. Come sempre, fatemi sapere cosa ne pensate qui sotto.

Het is niet de eerste keer dat ik aan boord ga van een Ritz Carlton Yacht. Ik heb een paar jaar geleden hun vorige schip, de Evrima, geprobeerd. Er waren nogal wat kinderziektes aan boord van die cruise, dus ik ben benieuwd hoe ze zijn veranderd (of dat ze dat al zijn!) met de toevoeging van Ilma en Luminara. snippet.title: How do Minecraft computers work?
snippet.description:
Today I learn to build Minecraft redstone computers, with expert lesson from Computational Redstone YouTuber  @mattbatwings   . Mattbatwings has built pacman in Minecraft, Super Mario Bros in Minecraft, Flappy bird in Minecraft and so much more - a lot of these giant redstone contraptions are featured in this video. Matt also does a tutorial on Computational redstone, covering the fundaments of Minecraft redstone logic, and even gets me to build my first computational redstone contraption.

MATTS CHANNEL: https://www.youtube.com/@mattbatwings
GO WATCH EVERYTHING HE HAS MADE!!

Mattbatwings ha costruito Pacman in Minecraft, Super Mario Bros in Minecraft, Flappy Bird in Minecraft e molto altro ancora: molti di questi giganteschi congegni in redstone sono presenti in questo video. Matt realizza anche un tutorial sulla redstone computazionale, che illustra i fondamenti della logica della redstone di Minecraft, e mi fa persino costruire il mio primo congegno in redstone computazionale.

CANALE DI MATTS: https://www.youtube.com/@mattbatwings
ANDATE A GUARDARE TUTTO CIÒ CHE HA CREATO!!

es-US.title: ¿Cómo funcionan las computadoras de Minecraft?
es-US.description:
Hoy aprendo a construir computadoras de redstone para Minecraft, con la lección experta del YouTuber de Redstone Computacional @mattbatwings. Mattbatwings ha creado Pacman, Super Mario Bros., Flappy Bird y muchos más en Minecraft; muchos de estos artefactos gigantes de redstone aparecen en este video. Matt también hace un tutorial sobre redstone computacional, que abarca los fundamentos de la lógica de redstone para Minecraft, e incluso me ayuda a construir mi primer artefacto de redstone computacional.

CANAL DE MATTS: https://www.youtube.com/@mattbatwings
¡VAYAN A VER TODO LO QUE HA CREADO!

snippet.title: Search and recovery efforts continue across the flood ravaged Hill Country
snippet.description:
Flash floods in Texas killed at least 82 people over the Fourth of July holiday weekend and left others still missing, including girls attending a summer camp. The devastation along the Guadalupe River, outside of San Antonio, has drawn a massive search effort as officials face questions over their preparedness and the speed of their initial actions.

snippet.description:
Check out highlights from the 2025 British Grand Prix as Lando Norris emerges victorious to mark his first win at Silverstone. McLaren teammate Oscar Piastri was stripped of his chance of victory by a 10-second penalty for a safety car infringement, but still claimed second place in the race. Nico Hulkenberg claimed the first podium of his 239-race career.

मेरे दोस्त और मैं महंगी वस्तुओं को रखने के लिए एक दूसरे से प्रतिस्पर्धा करते थे, यह देखने के लिए कि कौन उन्हें सबसे अच्छी तरह से साफ कर सकता है!
मुझे Instagram पर फ़ॉलो करें💕 https://www.instagram.com/kathleen.hixson

id.title: Jika Anda membersihkannya, itu milik Anda!
id.description:
Saya dan teman-teman saling berlomba untuk menjaga barang-barang mahal dengan melihat siapa yang paling jago membersihkannya!
Follow saya di Instagram💕 https://www.instagram.com/kathleen.hixson

ru.title: Если ты уберешь, это твое!
ru.description:
Мы с друзьями соревновались друг с другом, кто лучше всех сможет их почистить, чтобы сохранить дорогие вещи!
Подписывайтесь на меня в Instagram💕 https://www.instagram.com/kathleen.hixson

ko.title: 그것을 청소하면, 그것은 당신의 것입니다!
ko.description:
친구들과 함께 누가 비싼 물건들을 가장 잘 닦는지 경쟁하며 소중한 물건을 지켜냈어요!
인스타그램에서 팔로우하세요💕 https://www.instagram.com/kathleen.hixson

ar.title: إذا قمت بتنظيفه، فهو لك!
ar.description: تنافستُ أنا وأصدقائي على الحفاظ على الأغراض الثمينة، من ينظفها أفضل! تابعوني على إنستغرام💕https://www.instagram.com/kathleen.hixson

de.title: Wenn du es reinigst, gehört es dir!
de.description:
Meine Freunde und ich wetteiferten darum, wer teure Gegenstände am besten reinigen konnte!
Folgt mir auf Instagram💕 https://www.instagram.com/kathleen.hixson

fr.title: Si tu le nettoies, tu le gardes !
fr.description:
Mes amis et moi avons rivalisé pour conserver des objets coûteux en voyant qui les nettoyait le mieux !
Suivez-moi sur Instagram 💕 https://www.instagram.com/kathleen.hixson

vi.title: Nếu bạn dọn dẹp nó, bạn sẽ giữ nó!
vi.description:
Tôi và bạn bè đã thi nhau giữ những món đồ đắt tiền bằng cách xem ai có thể vệ sinh chúng sạch sẽ nhất!
Hãy theo dõi tôi trên Instagram💕 https://www.instagram.com/kathleen.hixson

it.title: Se lo pulisci, lo tieni!
it.description:
Io e le mie amiche abbiamo fatto a gara per conservare gli oggetti più preziosi, vedendo chi li puliva meglio!
Seguimi su Instagram💕 https://www.instagram.com/kathleen.hixson

es.title: ¡Si lo limpias, lo mantienes!
es.description:
Mis amigas y yo competimos para conservar objetos caros, ¡a ver quién los limpiaba mejor!
Síganme en Instagram💕 https://www.instagram.com/kathleen.hixson

snippet.title: Death toll in central Texas flash floods rises to 79 as sheriff says 10 campers remain missing
snippet.description:
Families sifted through waterlogged debris Sunday and stepped inside empty cabins at Camp Mystic, an all-girls summer camp ripped apart by flash floods that washed homes off their foundations and killed at least 79 people in central Texas.

Rescuers maneuvering through challenging terrain continued their desperate search for the missing, including 10 girls and a counselor from the camp. For the first time since the storms began pounding Texas, Gov. Greg Abbott said there were 41 people confirmed to be unaccounted for across the state and more could be missing.

Read more at: https://www.9news.com/article/news/nation-world/texas-floods-campers-missing/507-2c41ffb5-638c-4d53-bc6b-a444a0618bdb

snippet.title: Texas flooding timelapse: Guadalupe River jumps 19 feet an an hour
snippet.description:
In less than an hour, the Guadalupe River in Texas went from 1 1/2 feet to 20 feet. As of Monday morning, 82 are confirmed to have died with another ten still missing.

snippet.title: The evidence that damned Piastri in Verstappen British GP controversy
snippet.description:
A penalty for erratic driving decided the British Grand Prix as an aggrieved Oscar Piastri lost victory to McLaren team-mate and F1 title rival Lando Norris. 

This wet and wild Silverstone F1 race came down to one key moment: the restart on lap 21, when Piastri’s braking caught Verstappen out. Jon Noble and Scott Mitchell-Malm delve into the data that doomed Piastri.

01:43 Piastri's double trouble
03:10 Verstappen's view
04:17 Why Canada was different
05:40 McLaren suggests gamesmanship
07:48 Piastri's cheeky swap request
08:46 Title race implications

fr-FR.title: Le travail du métal commence sur le camion à pommes de terre de Matt !
fr-FR.description:
La promotion onX Offroad du 4 juillet est toujours en cours ! Bénéficiez de 50 % de réduction sur la meilleure application de cartographie des sentiers avec le code FOJ25 sur http://onxmaps.com/offroad et débloquez plus de 1 050 000 kilomètres de sentiers, de campings et d'outils d'aventure hors réseau. En vous inscrivant, envoyez un e-mail à merchsupport@robbylayton.com. Pour chaque tranche de 5 $ dépensée avec onX, nous vous offrons une participation au tirage au sort du C10 1972 ! Le paiement de chaque commande est toujours valable, et le ticket d'or d'une valeur de 1 000 $ est toujours à gagner sur http://www.robbylayton.com.

On est de retour sur le Spud Truck de Matt ! 🛠️ Robby et son équipe se mettent au travail dès aujourd'hui pour s'attaquer à la prochaine étape importante de la construction du Spud Truck ! Tout le monde est sur le pont : métallerie, débosselage, martelage, retrait de clés, soudure, meulage et ponçage pour que cette bête soit prête à être peinte. On progresse sérieusement, mais il reste une grande décision à prendre…

De quelle couleur le peindre ? 🎨 Partagez vos idées de couleurs dans les commentaires : nous avons besoin de votre aide pour choisir !

ja.title: マットのスパッドトラックの金属加工が始まります!
ja.description:
onX Offroad 7月4日セール、まだ開催中！ http://onxmaps.com/offroad でコード FOJ25 を入力すると、最高のトレイルマッピングアプリが50%オフ！さらに、65万マイル（約100万キロ）以上のトレイル、キャンプ場、オフグリッドアドベンチャーツールがアンロックされます。ご登録は merchsupport@robbylayton.com までメールでお送りください。onXで5ドルお買い上げごとに、’72 C10 プレゼントへの応募権をプレゼント！ ご注文ごとに現金プレゼント！ 1,000ドル相当のゴールデンチケットも引き続き http://www.robbylayton.com で販売中です。

MattのSpud Truckに戻ってきました！🛠️ Robbyとクルーは今日、Spud Truck製作の次の大きな段階に着手するため、全力で作業を開始しました！金属加工、へこみ直し、ハンマー打ち、鍵抜き、溶接、研磨、サンディングなど、このモンスターを塗装に一歩近づけるために、全員で取り組んでいます。着々と進んでいますが、まだ大きな決断が残っています…

ko.title: 맷의 스퍼드 트럭에서 금속 작업이 시작되었습니다!
ko.description:

맷의 스퍼드 트럭으로 돌아왔습니다! 🛠️ 오늘 로비와 팀원들이 스퍼드 트럭 제작의 다음 단계를 본격적으로 시작합니다! 금속 작업, 덴트 제거, 망치질, 열쇠 뽑기, 용접, 연삭, 샌딩까지 모든 과정을 수작업으로 진행하여 이 괴물을 도색 직전까지 몰고 갑니다. 상당한 진전을 보이고 있지만, 중요한 결정이 하나 남았습니다…

pl.title: Rozpoczęto obróbkę metalu przy ciężarówce do ziemniaków Matta!
pl.description:
Wyprzedaż onX Offroad z okazji 4 lipca wciąż trwa! Zdobądź 50% zniżki na najlepszą aplikację do mapowania szlaków, używając kodu FOJ25 na http://onxmaps.com/offroad i odblokuj ponad 650 000 mil szlaków, kempingów i narzędzi do przygód poza siecią. Jeśli się zarejestrujesz, napisz na adres merchsupport@robbylayton.com, a za każde 5 USD wydane w onX otrzymasz wstęp do rozdania nagród C10 z 1972 roku! Pieniądze z każdego zamówienia nadal trafiają na złoty bilet o wartości 1000, który wciąż jest do zdobycia na http://www.robbylayton.com

Wracamy do Spud Truck Matta! 🛠️ Robby i ekipa od razu zabrali się do pracy, ponieważ podejmujemy się kolejnego dużego etapu budowy Spud Truck! Wszyscy są na pokładzie, zajmując się obróbką metalu, usuwaniem wgnieceń, młotkowaniem, wyrywaniem kluczy, spawaniem, szlifowaniem i polerowaniem, aby zbliżyć tę bestię o krok do pomalowania. Robimy poważne postępy — ale pozostała jeszcze jedna ważna decyzja...

Jaki kolor powinniśmy pomalować? 🎨 Podzielcie się swoimi pomysłami na kolor w komentarzach — potrzebujemy Waszej pomocy w podjęciu decyzji!

snippet.title: Texas flooding survivor & witness reaction to Kerrville damage, search & rescues: 'Complete shock'
snippet.description:
A Kerrville resident said he and his wife were taken 200 feet down the Guadalupe River and managed to survive while his home was damaged by the flooding.

"It was scary," Scott Walden said while describing the speed of which the water rose. "It was really scary."

Meanwhile, a Pennsylvania woman visiting family in the area said she remains in shock, especially given the volume of missing adults and children, many from Camp Mystic.

"It's not going to be a good ending," Tonia Fucci said. "There's no way people could have survived the swiftness of the water."

snippet.title: Cyberpunk: Edgerunners 2 | Official Teaser | Netflix
snippet.description:
David is dead. But Night City lives on.
Cyberpunk: Edgerunners 2 is now in production!

Cyberpunk: Edgerunners 2 presents a new standalone 10-episode story from the world of Cyberpunk 2077— a raw chronicle of redemption and revenge. In a city that thrives in the spotlight of violence, one question remains: when the world is blinded by spectacle, what extremes do you have to go to make your story matter?

Director Kai Ikarashi (Cyberpunk: Edgerunners, SSSS.Gridman) brings a bold, cinematic vision to the series, supported by the lead character designer Kanno Ichigo (Promare, Cyberpunk: Edgerunners). They're joined by returning collaborators Masahiko Otsuka (Gurren Lagann, Promare) and Hugo Award winner Bartosz Sztybor as Showrunner, Story Writer, and Producer.

Cyberpunk: Edgerunners 2 is created in collaboration with CD PROJEKT RED and animation studio TRIGGER, with a planned release on Netflix in the future.

snippet.title: Belton, Texas teen rescued from deadly Guadalupe River floods
snippet.description:
BELTON, Texas (KWTX) - Belton teenager Riata Schoepf was rescue by first responders on Friday after being swept away by the deadly Guadalupe River floods.

Riata went on vacation to Hunt, Texas with another family for the Fourth of July. Their hotel bordered the Guadalupe River. Her dad, Ronnie Schoepf, recalled his daughters experience being evacuated.

“She says around 2:30 or so she’s hearing loud thunder and lightning and then the next thing she knew somebody’s banging on her door telling everybody they need to get out,” Ronnie said.

Riata and her group took to their vehicles to escape the flooding, but traffic was at a standstill. Water then began to rise around their car.

snippet.title: Cyberpunk: Edgerunners 2 | Announcement Teaser
snippet.description:
David is dead. But Night City lives on.

Cyberpunk: Edgerunners 2 is now in production!

Cyberpunk: Edgerunners 2 presents a new standalone 10-episode story from the world of Cyberpunk 2077— a raw chronicle of redemption and revenge. In a city that thrives in the spotlight of violence, one question remains: when the world is blinded by spectacle, what extremes do you have to go to make your story matter?

Director Kai Ikarashi (Cyberpunk: Edgerunners, SSSS.Gridman) brings a bold, cinematic vision to the series, supported by the lead character designer Kanno Ichigo (Promare, Cyberpunk: Edgerunners). They're joined by returning collaborators Masahiko Otsuka (Gurren Lagann, Promare) and Hugo Award winner Bartosz Sztybor as Showrunner, Story Writer, and Producer.

Cyberpunk: Edgerunners 2 is created in collaboration with CD PROJEKT RED and animation studio TRIGGER, with a planned release on Netflix in the future.

Music: “Dive” by Beach House. Licensed courtesy of Sub Pop Records.

Stay connected, choom:

zh-Hans.title: 《赛博朋克：边缘行者2》｜先导预告片
zh-Hans.description:
大卫已逝，但夜之城永不停歇。

《赛博朋克：边缘行者 2》正式开启制作！

《赛博朋克：边缘行者 2》将带来一个全新的独立10集故事，延续《赛博朋克 2077》的世界观 —— 一段关于救赎与复仇的残酷传奇。在这座因暴力而闪耀的城市里，一个问题始终萦绕：当世界被浮华蒙蔽双眼，你究竟要付出何等代价，才能让自己的故事被人铭记？

本季由导演 五十岚海（《赛博朋克：边缘行者》《SSSS.古立特》）倾力打造，以大胆的影视化风格呈现；主角设计由 菅野一期（《普罗米亚》《赛博朋克：边缘行者》）操刀。剧本团队包括回归的 大冢雅彦（《天元突破红莲螺岩》《普罗米亚》）与雨果奖得主 Bartosz Sztybor。

《赛博朋克：边缘行者 2》由 CD PROJEKT RED 与动画工作室 TRIGGER 联合制作，目前正在开发中，计划未来登陆 Netflix 平台。

音乐 Beach House 的《Dive》，经 Sub Pop Records 授权。

https://www.instagram.com/edgerunners/

fr.title: Cyberpunk : Edgerunners 2 | Teaser d'annonce
fr.description:
David est mort. Mais Night City continue de vivre.

Cyberpunk : Edgerunners 2 est désormais en production !

Cyberpunk : Edgerunners 2 présente une nouvelle histoire indépendante en 10 épisodes issue de l'univers de Cyberpunk 2077, une chronique crue sur la rédemption et la vengeance. Dans une ville qui prospère sous les feux de la violence, une question demeure : lorsque le monde est aveuglé par le spectacle, jusqu'où êtes-vous prêt à aller pour que votre histoire compte ?

Le réalisateur Kai Ikarashi (Cyberpunk: Edgerunners, SSSS.Gridman) apporte une vision cinématographique audacieuse à la série, soutenu par le character designer principal Kanno Ichigo (Promare, Cyberpunk: Edgerunners). Ils sont rejoints par des collaborateurs de longue date, Masahiko Otsuka (Gurren Lagann, Promare) et Bartosz Sztybor, lauréat du prix Hugo, en tant que showrunner, scénariste et producteur.

Cyberpunk: Edgerunners 2 est créé en collaboration avec CD PROJEKT RED et le studio d'animation TRIGGER, et sa sortie est prévue prochainement sur Netflix.

Musique : « Dive » par Beach House. Sous licence de Sub Pop Records.

https://www.instagram.com/cdprojektred_fr/

ru.title: Cyberpunk: Edgerunners 2 | Анонсирующий тизер-трейлер
ru.description:
Дэвид мёртв. Но жизнь в Найт-Сити продолжается. 

Аниме-сериал Cyberpunk: Edgerunners 2 уже в производстве.

Cyberpunk: Edgerunners 2 — это новая самостоятельная история о мести и искуплении во вселенной Cyberpunk 2077. Вас ждет 10 серий.
В городе, что пышет жестокостью, остается ответить лишь на один вопрос: когда мир жаждет зрелищ, на что ты готов пойти, чтобы оставить свой след?

Режиссер Кай Игараси (Cyberpunk: Edgerunners, SSSS.Gridman) привнес в аниме-сериал смелое, кинематографическое видение, которое ведущий дизайнер персонажей Канно Ичиго («Промар», Cyberpunk: Edgerunners) воплотит в своем визуальном стиле. В качестве сценаристов к ним присоединятся Масахико Оцука («Гуррен-Лаганн», «Промар») и лауреат премии «Хьюго» Бартош Штыбор.

Музыка: "Dive" группы Beach House. Лицензия предоставлена с разрешения Sub Pop Records.

pt-BR.description:
David está morto. Mas Night City continua viva.

Cyberpunk: Edgerunners 2 está em produção!

Cyberpunk: Edgerunners 2 apresenta uma nova história independente em 10 episódios no mundo de Cyberpunk 2077 — uma crônica intensa de redenção e vingança. Em uma cidade que prospera sob os holofotes da violência, uma pergunta permanece: quando o mundo está cego pelo espetáculo, até quais extremos você precisa ir para que sua história importe?

O diretor Kai Ikarashi (Cyberpunk: Mercenários, SSSS.Gridman) traz uma visão cinematográfica ousada para a série, com apoio do líder de design de personagens Kanno Ichigo (Promare, Cyberpunk: Mercenários). Eles se unem a colaboradores já conhecidos: Masahiko Otsuka (Gurren Lagann, Promare) e o vencedor do Prêmio Hugo, Bartosz Sztybor, como showrunner, roteirista e produtor.

Produzido em colaboração entre a CD PROJEKT RED e o estúdio de animação TRIGGER, Cyberpunk: Edgerunners 2 tem lançamento previsto na Netflix.

pl.title: Cyberpunk: Edgerunners 2 | Zapowiedź
pl.description:
David nie żyje. Ale w Night City życie toczy się dalej.

Ruszyła produkcja Cyberpunk: Edgerunners 2!

Cyberpunk: Edgerunners 2 to nowa historia ze świata Cyberpunka 2077, zamknięta w 10 odcinkach, która opowie o zemście i odkupieniu. W mieście, w którym przemoc jest na porządku dziennym, a ludzie dbają tylko o pozory, każdy zadaje sobie to jedno pytanie: jak daleko trzeba się posunąć, by twoja historia coś znaczyła?

Reżyser Kai Ikarashi (Cyberpunk: Edgerunners, SSSS.Gridman) wnosi do serii swoją śmiałą, filmową wizję. Wesprą go projektant postaci Kanno Ichigo (Promare, Cyberpunk: Edgerunners) oraz Masahiko Otsuka (Gurren Lagann, Promare), odpowiedzialny za adaptację historii na potrzeby anime w studiu TRIGGER. W roli scenarzysty oraz showrunnera powróci także laureat nagrody Hugo Awards, Bartosz Sztybor. 

Cyberpunk: Edgerunners 2 powstaje we współpracy CD PROJEKT RED oraz studia TRIGGER i zadebiutuje w przyszłości na platformie Netflix.

Muzyka: "Dive" autorstwa Beach House. Licencja dzięki uprzejmości Sub Pop Records.

ko.title: 사이버펑크: 엣지러너 2 | 공개 티저
ko.description:
데이비드는 죽었다. 그럼에도 나이트 시티의 삶은 계속된다.

사이버펑크: 엣지러너 2를 제작 중입니다!

사이버펑크: 엣지러너 2는 사이버펑크 2077의 세계를 배경으로 한 새로운 스탠드얼론 애니메이션이며, 10개의 에피소드로 구성된 복수와 구원의 연대기입니다. 폭력이 스포트라이트를 받는 도시에서 남는 질문은 하나뿐입니다. 세상이 눈부신 볼거리에 눈이 멀었을 때, 자신의 이야기를 세상에 남기려면 어디까지 가야 할까요?

이카라시 카이 감독(사이버펑크: 엣지러너, SSSS.Gridman)이 시리즈에 대담하고 영화적인 비전을 불어넣고, 칸노 이치고(프로메어, 사이버펑크: 엣지러너)가 리드 캐릭터 디자이너로 함께합니다. 여기에 오츠카 마사히코 (그렌라간, 프로메어)와 휴고 상 수상 작가 바르토시 슈티보르가 총괄 책임자이자 스토리 작가와 프로듀서 역할로 다시 합류합니다.

사이버펑크: 엣지러너 2는 CD 프로젝트 레드와 애니메이션 스튜디오 TRIGGER가 함께 제작하며, Netflix를 통해 출시됩니다.

ja.title: サイバーパンク: エッジランナーズ２ | アナウンスメントティーザー
ja.description:
デイビッドは死んだ。だがナイトシティは生き続ける。

『サイバーパンク: エッジランナーズ２』鋭意制作中！

『サイバーパンク: エッジランナーズ２』は、ゲーム「サイバーパンク2077」の世界を舞台とした、10話構成の新たなオリジナルアニメーションシリーズ。これは贖罪と復讐の生々しい記録。暴力を糧に煌々と輝く、“伝説”を見慣れた街。その中で、人は一体何をもって己の物語を語るのか。
監督 五十嵐海 (『サイバーパンク: エッジランナーズ』『SSSS.GRIDMAN』) が作品全体を大胆かつシネマティックに構成。その脇を固めるのは、リードキャラクターデザイナー 菅野一期（『プロメア』『サイバーパンク: エッジランナーズ』）。前作同様、大塚雅彦（『天元突破グレンラガン』『プロメア』）とバルトシュ・シュティボル（ヒューゴー賞受賞作家、本作ではショーランナー＆プロデューサーも担当）がタッグを組み、脚本を手掛ける。

『サイバーパンク: エッジランナーズ２』はCD PROJEKT REDとTRIGGERが共同で贈るアニメシリーズ。Netflixにて配信予定。

音楽：「Dive」 by Beach House
ライセンス提供：Sub Pop Records

snippet.title: Texas Flood Tragedy: Husband Swept Away While Camping, Wife Still Missing | Kerr County Devastation
snippet.description:
A heartbreaking story out of Kerr County, Texas, where catastrophic flooding has displaced families and left many searching for loved ones. Brian Eids recounts the terrifying moment floodwaters swept him and his wife away from their campsite — he survived, but she remains missing. 

This report from KXAN’s Brianna Hollis captures the emotional toll as survivors gather at a reunification center in Ingram, desperately seeking updates. Governor Greg Abbott is expected to speak later tonight.

snippet.title: SPIRIT EMPRESS: Two Forms, One Card!
snippet.description:
X ► https://twitter.com/ClashRoyale/
Instagram ► https://www.instagram.com/clashroyale
TikTok ► https://www.tiktok.com/@clashroyale
Facebook ► https://www.facebook.com/ClashRoyale/

ENTER THE ARENA
Build your Battle Deck and outsmart the enemy in fast real-time battles. From the creators of CLASH OF CLANS comes a real-time multiplayer battle game starring your favourite Clash characters and more. Start battling against players from around the world!

BECOME A MASTER OF STRATEGY AND DECK BUILDING
Choose unique Cards to your Battle Deck and head to the Arena for Battle!
Place your Cards right and knock down the enemy King and Princesses from their Towers in a strategic and fast-paced match.

COLLECT AND UPGRADE 100+ CARDS
Hog Rider! Collect and upgrade 100+ Cards featuring the Clash of Clans troops, spells and defences you know and love and many others. Win battles and progress to new Arenas to unlock powerful new Cards to your collection!

BATTLE YOUR WAY TO THE TOP
Battle your way to the League and Global Tournaments to match against the best players in the world.
Compete for glory and rewards!

SEASONAL EVENTS
Unlock new Seasonal items like Tower Skins, Emotes and powerful Magic Items with the Season Pass and participate in fun Challenges that put your skills to the test!

JOIN A CLAN AND GO TO WAR
Join or form a Clan with other players to share Cards and battle in Clan Wars for BIG rewards!

See you in the Arena!
#ClashRoyale

snippet.title: Jason Momoa Causes CHAOS in the Pit at Ozzy Osbourne's Final Show
snippet.description:
We knew this show would be legendary, and Birmingham did not disappoint! This massive event was a monumental celebration of Ozzy Osborne and Black Sabbath, featuring a "who's who" of rock royalty. We witnessed incredible performances from Lizzy Hale, Papa V's epic "Bark at the Moon," Alice in Chains, and Lamb of God. The Slayer reunion, honoring Black Sabbath and Ozzy, was absolutely showstopping.

But the moment that truly broke the internet? Host Jason Momoa, during Pantera's absolutely crushing set, couldn't resist the call of the pit! He jumped in, completely lost in the moment, joining the mosh pit for Pantera's entire performance of "Hostel." Eyewitnesses saw him hugging fans and taking selfies – a true testament to his love for the music. This historic party in Birmingham is still rocking, and Jason Momoa's sincerity and passion are undeniable!

pa.title: 45 ਕਿਲੋ ਘਟਾਓ, $250,000 ਜਿੱਤੋ!
pa.description:
**ਕੋਚ ਟਾਈਲਰ ਵਾਲ ਦੀ ਪਿਆਰ ਭਰੀ ਯਾਦ ਵਿੱਚ**

ਬਹੁਤ ਹੀ ਦੁਖ ਭਰੀ ਸੂਚਨਾ ਦੇ ਨਾਲ ਅਸੀਂ ਤੁਹਾਨੂੰ ਦੱਸ ਰਹੇ ਹਾਂ ਕਿ ਕੋਚ ਟਾਈਲਰ ਵਾਲ ਹੁਣ ਸਾਡੇ ਵਿਚ ਨਹੀਂ ਰਹੇ। ਕੋਚ ਵਾਲ ਇਕ ਬੇਮਿਸਾਲ ਇਨਸਾਨ ਸਨ, ਜਿਨ੍ਹਾਂ ਦੀ ਦਇਆਲਤਾ ਅਤੇ ਖੁਸ਼ਮਿਜਾਜ਼ੀ ਨੇ ਉਨ੍ਹਾਂ ਨੂੰ ਮਿਲਣ ਵਾਲੇ ਹਰ ਵਿਅਕਤੀ ਦੇ ਦਿਲ ਨੂੰ ਛੋਹ ਲਿਆ।
ਉਹਨਾਂ ਦੇ ਅਚਾਨਕ ਵਿਛੋੜੇ ਨੇ ਸਾਡੇ ਦਿਲਾਂ ਨੂੰ ਗਮੀ ਨਾਲ ਭਰ ਦਿੱਤਾ ਹੈ।

ਇਸ ਦੁਖਦਾਈ ਘੜੀ 'ਚ, ਅਸੀਂ ਕੋਚ ਵਾਲ ਦੇ ਪਰਿਵਾਰ ਨਾਲ ਸੰਪਰਕ ਕੀਤਾ
ਜਿਸ ਵਿੱਚ ਉਨ੍ਹਾਂ ਨੇ ਬਹੁਤ ਸਹਿਣਸ਼ੀਲਤਾ ਅਤੇ ਸਿਆਣਪ ਨਾਲ ਸਾਨੂੰ ਦੱਸਿਆ ਕਿ
ਟਾਈਲਰ ਚਾਹੁੰਦੇ ਸਨ ਕਿ ਉਨ੍ਹਾਂ ਦੀ ਆਸ ਅਤੇ ਸਕਾਰਾਤਮਕਤਾ ਭਰੀ ਸੋਚ ਲੋਕਾਂ ਤੱਕ ਪਹੁੰਚਦੀ ਰਹੇ, ਭਾਵੇਂ ਉਹ ਸਾਢੇ ਨਾਮ ਹੋਣ ਜਾਂ ਨਾ ਹੋਣ।

ਅਸੀਂ ਨਿਮਰਤਾ ਨਾਲ ਬੇਨਤੀ ਕਰਦੇ ਹਾਂ ਕਿ ਤੁਸੀਂ ਕੋਚ ਵਾਲ ਦੀ ਯਾਦ ਨੂੰ ਸਨਮਾਨ ਦਿਓ
ਅਤੇ ਇਸ ਮੁਸ਼ਕਲ ਸਮੇਂ 'ਚ ਉਨ੍ਹਾਂ ਦੇ ਪਰਿਵਾਰ ਦੀ ਨਿੱਜੀ ਜ਼ਿੰਦਗੀ ਦੀ ਇੱਜ਼ਤ ਕਰੋ।

ਕੋਚ ਟਾਈਲਰ ਵਾਲ ਦੀ ਹੌਂਸਲੇ ਅਤੇ ਦਿਲਾਸੇ ਭਰੀ ਵਿਰਾਸਤ
ਹਮੇਸ਼ਾ ਉਨ੍ਹਾਂ ਲੋਕਾਂ ਦੇ ਦਿਲਾਂ ਵਿੱਚ ਜੀਵੰਤ ਰਹੇਗੀ, ਜਿਨ੍ਹਾਂ ਨੂੰ ਉਹਨਾਂ ਨੂੰ ਜਾਣਨ ਦਾ ਸੌਭਾਗ ਮਿਲਿਆ।

ਜਿਸ ਕਾਰੋਬਾਰ ਦੇ ਤੁਸੀਂ ਸਪਨੇ ਦੇਖ ਰਹੇ ਹੋ, ਉਹ ਸ਼ੁਰੂ ਕਰੋ –

te.description:
కోచ్ టైలర్ వాల్ కు ప్రేమతో సమర్పణ

కోచ్ టైలర్ వాల్ అనుకోని రీతిలో ఈ లోకాన్ని విడిచిన విషాదవార్తను తెలియజేయడం చాలా బాధాకరం. కోచ్ వాల్ అందరి హృదయాలను తాకిన మానవత్వం, దయామయమైన వ్యక్తిత్వం కలిగిన అసాధారణ వ్యక్తి.

ఈ విషాదకర సంఘటన అనంతరం, ఈ వీడియోను పంచుకోవాలా వద్దా అనే విషయంలో కోచ్ వాల్ కుటుంబాన్ని సంప్రదించాం. వారి తెలివైన మరియు పరిపక్వమైన స్పందనలో, ""టైలర్ ఆశాభావం మరియు సానుకూలతను ప్రపంచానికి చేరవేయాలనే తన ఆకాంక్ష ఈ సమయంలో కూడా కొనసాగాలి"" అని చెప్పారు.

ఈ కష్ట సమయంలో, మీరు కోచ్ వాల్ యొక్క జ్ఞాపకాన్ని గౌరవించి, ఆయన కుటుంబానికి గౌరవంగా ప్రైవసీని కల్పించమని మనవి చేస్తున్నాము.

หลังจากข่าวที่น่าเศร้าโศกนี้ เราได้ติดต่อครอบครัวของโค้ชวอลล์เพื่อพิจารณาว่าควรแชร์วิดีโอนี้หรือไม่ พวกเขาแสดงความอบอุ่นและใจดีบวกกับความเชื่อว่าไทเลอร์ต้องการให้ข้อความแห่งความหวังและการคิดบวกของเขาส่งต่อไปยังผู้อื่นต่อไป แม้ว่าเขาจะไม่ได้อยู่ก็ตาม

เราขอความร่วมมืออย่างนอบน้อมว่าให้เคารพความทรงจำของโค้ชวอลล์และเคารพความต้องการความเป็นส่วนตัวของครอบครัวเขาในช่วงเวลาที่ยากลำบากนี้

มรดกแห่งความเห็นอกเห็นใจและกำลังใจของโค้ชไทเลอร์ วอลล์จะคงอยู่ในใจของทุกคนที่โชคดีพอที่มีโอกาสได้รู้จักเขา

ta.title: 45 கிலோ எடை குறைத்து, $250,000 வெல்லுங்கள்!
ta.description:
**கோச் டைலர் வால் அவர்களின் அன்பான நினைவாக**

கோச் டைலர் வால் அவர்களின் எதிர்பாராத மறைவுச் செய்தியை ஆழ்ந்த துக்கத்துடன் பகிர்ந்துகொள்கிறோம். கோச் வால் ஒரு அற்புதமான மனிதர், அவரது கருணையும் உண்மையான மனப்பான்மையும் அவரை அறிந்த அனைவரையும் கவர்ந்தது. அவரது இழப்பு எங்கள் இதயங்களை துயரத்தால் கனக்கச் செய்துள்ளது.

இந்தத் துயரச் செய்தியைத் தொடர்ந்து, இந்த வீடியோவை வெளியிட வேண்டுமா என்று கோச் வால் குடும்பத்தினரை அணுகினோம். அவர்கள், தங்கள் ஞானத்தோடும் பெருந்தன்மையோடும், டைலர் இல்லாத நிலையிலும் அவரது நம்பிக்கை மற்றும் நேர்மறையான செய்தி மற்றவர்களைச் சென்றடைய வேண்டும் என்று விரும்பியிருப்பார் எனத் தெரிவித்தனர்.

இந்தக் கடினமான நேரத்தில் கோச் வால் அவர்களின் நினைவைப் போற்றுமாறும், அவரது குடும்பத்தினரின் தனிப்பட்ட உரிமையை மதிக்குமாறும் தாழ்மையுடன் கேட்டுக்கொள்கிறோம்.

கோச் டைலர் வால் அவர்களின் இரக்கமும் ஊக்கமும் நிறைந்த மரபு, அவரை அறிந்த அனைவரின் இதயங்களிலும் நிலைத்திருக்கும்.

snippet.title: Musk’s political party: A political vision or personal rivalry with Trump? | DW News
snippet.description:
Tech billionaire Elon Musk says he has created a new political party in the United States, to challenge what he called the country's one-party system.
On the social platform X, the former ally of US President Donald Trump wrote he was forming the America Party, to give back Americans their freedom. He made the announcement after holding a 24-hour poll on the platform, where the majority voted in favor of the new party.

snippet.title: THE COMEBACK
snippet.description:
#getyourclashback This Summer Jam, Get Your Village Back in Shape.

Follow us on our Socials!
Twitter ► https://twitter.com/ClashofClans/
Instagram ► https://www.instagram.com/clashofclans 
Facebook ► https://www.facebook.com/ClashofClans 
TikTok ► https://www.tiktok.com/@clashofclans

Attack. Defend. Strategize. Download for free for mobile devices. supr.cl/PlayClashOfClans

From rage-­filled Barbarians with glorious mustaches to pyromaniac wizards, raise your own army and lead your clan to victory! Build your village to fend off raiders, battle against millions of players worldwide, and forge a powerful clan with others to destroy enemy clans.
PLEASE NOTE! Clash of Clans is free to download and play, however some game items can also be purchased for real money 

Also, under our Terms of Service and Privacy Policy, you must be at least 13 years of age to play or download Clash of Clans.
A network connection is also required.

FEATURES
- Build your village into an unbeatable fortress 
- Raise your own army of Barbarians, Archers, Hog Riders, Wizards, Dragons and other mighty fighters
- Battle with players worldwide and take their Trophies
- Join together with other players to form the ultimate Clan
- Fight against rival Clans in epic Clan Wars 
- Build 18 unique units with multiple levels of upgrades
- Discover your favorite attacking army from countless combinations of troops, spells, Heroes and Clan reinforcements 
- Defend your village with a multitude of Cannons, Towers, Mortars, Bombs, Traps and Walls
- Fight against the Goblin King in a campaign through the realm

Chief, are you having problems? Visit https://help.supercellsupport.com/clash-of-clans/en/

Privacy Policy:
https://supercell.com/en/privacy-policy/

Terms of Service:
https://supercell.com/en/terms-of-service/

Aujourd'hui, je découvre le nouveau membre de la sainte trinité des hypercars : une Porsche 918 Spyder de 2015. Et comme vous pouvez l'imaginer, c'est la pire de la planète. snippet.title: “Chainsaw Man – The Movie: Reze Arc” - Main Trailer／劇場版『チェンソーマン レゼ篇』本予告
snippet.description:
“Chainsaw Man – The Movie: Reze Arc” - Main Trailer／劇場版『チェンソーマン レゼ篇』本予告

劇場版『チェンソーマン レゼ篇』2025年9月19日（金） 全国公開 
主題歌 ： 米津玄師　「IRIS OUT」（Sony Music Labels Inc.） 

🎥劇場限定特典付き！ムビチケカード7月18日（金）より全国の上映劇場にて発売！
＜購入特典＞数量限定！ “チェンソーマン＆レゼ”両面クリアファイル
販売価格：1,500円（税込）
販売場所：全国の上映劇場
劇場リスト：https://theater.toho.co.jp/toho_theaterlist/chainsawman_reze.html

=============== 
＜劇場版『チェンソーマン レゼ篇』＞ 

◼︎INTRODUCTION 
恋も欲望も、人間も悪魔も全てを巻き込むド派手な血戦、劇場アニメ化！ 

シリーズ累計発行部数3,000万を突破し、現在「少年ジャンプ+」（集英社）で人気連載中の
漫画『チェンソーマン』（箸・藤本タツキ）。
2022年には、アニメスタジオMAPPA（代表作：『呪術廻戦』『進撃の巨人 The Final Season』等）による
制作のTVアニメが放送され、大きな話題を呼んだ同作。
そして2025年、連載当時大熱狂を巻き起こしたエピソードが劇場アニメ化！

◼︎STORY 
悪魔の心臓を持つ「チェンソーマン」となり、
公安対魔特異４課に所属するデビルハンターの少年・デンジ（戸谷菊之介）。
憧れのマキマ（楠木ともり）とのデートで浮かれている中、急な雨に見舞われ、
雨宿りしていると偶然“レゼ”（上田麗奈）という少女と出会った。
近所のカフェで働いているという彼女はデンジに優しく微笑み、二人は急速に親密に。
この出会いを境に、デンジの日常は変わり始めていく…… 

◼︎STAFF
原作：藤本タツキ（集英社「少年ジャンプ+」連載）
監督：𠮷原達矢　　　
脚本：瀬古浩司
キャラクターデザイン：杉山和隆
副監督：中園真登
サブキャラクターデザイン：山﨑爽太／駿　　
メインアニメーター：庄一
アクションディレクター：重次創太
悪魔デザイン：松浦力／押山清高
衣装デザイン：山本彩　　
美術監督：竹田悠介
色彩設計：中野尚美
カラースクリプト：りく
3DCGディレクター：渡辺大貴／玉井真広　　
撮影監督：伊藤哲平
編集：吉武将人
音響監督：名倉靖
音楽：牛尾憲輔
配給：東宝
制作：MAPPA　　
主題歌 ： 米津玄師「IRIS OUT」（Sony Music Labels Inc.）

◼︎CAST
デンジ：戸谷菊之介
ポチタ：井澤詩織
マキマ：楠木ともり
早川アキ：坂田将吾
パワー：ファイルーズあい
東山コベニ：高橋花林
ビーム：花江夏樹
暴力の魔人：内田夕夜
天使の悪魔：内田真礼
岸辺：津田健次郎
副隊長：高橋英則
野茂：赤羽根健治
謎の男：乃村健次
台風の悪魔：喜多村英梨
レゼ：上田麗奈

◼︎INTRODUCTION
Extravagant bloody battle involving love and desire, humans and devils, is coming to the big screens! 

“Chainsaw Man” is a manga serialized in Shueisha’s “Shonen Jump+” that has sold over 30,000,000 copies. In 2022, the series was broadcast as a TV Anime series that was made by animation studio MAPPA (Notable works: “JUJUTSU KAISEN”, “Attack on Titan Final Season”, etc.), creating buzz all over the world.
Now in 2025, the episode that made the world go wild during its serialization is coming to theaters as an animated movie!

◼︎STORY
Denji (Kikunosuke Toya) became “Chainsaw Man”, a boy with a devil’s heart, and is now part of Special Division 4’s devil hunters. After a date with Makima (Tomori Kusunoki), the woman of his dreams, Denji takes shelter from the rain and meets a girl called Reze (Reina Ueda).
The girl, who works at a nearby café, gives him a gentle smile, and they quickly grow close.
From this encounter onward, Denji's everyday life begins to change.

[STAFF]
Original Story: Tatsuki Fujimoto (Serialized in Shueisha's "Shonen Jump+")
Director: Tatsuya Yoshihara
Screenwriter: Hiroshi Seko
Character Designer: Kazutaka Sugiyama
Assistant Director: Masato Nakazono
Sub Character Designer: Souta Yamazaki, Shun
Main Animator: Shoichi
Action Animation Director: Sota Shigetsugu
Devil Designer: Riki Matsuura, Kiyotaka Oshiyama
Costume Designer: Aya Yamamoto
Art Director: Yusuke Takeda
Color Designer: Naomi Nakano
Color Script: Riku
3DCG Director: Daiki Watanabe, Masahiro Tamai
Compositing Director: Teppei Ito
Editor: Masato Yoshitake
Sound Director: Yasushi Nagura
Music: Kensuke Ushio
Distribution: TOHO
Production: MAPPA
Theme Song: Kenshi Yonezu “IRIS OUT" (Sony Music Labels Inc.)

[CAST]
Denji: Kikunosuke Toya
Pochita: Shiori Izawa
Makima: Tomori Kusunoki
Aki: Shogo Sakata
Power: Fairouz Ai
Kobeni: Karin Takahashi
Beam: Natsuki Hanae
Violence Fiend: Yuuya Uchida
Angel Devil: Maaya Uchida
Reze: Reina Ueda

劇場版公式サイト：https://chainsawman.dog/movie_reze/
TV版公式サイト：https://chainsawman.dog/tvseries/
公式X：@CHAINSAWMAN_PR（https://twitter.com/ CHAINSAWMAN_PR）
© 2025 MAPPA／チェンソーマンプロジェクト ©藤本タツキ／集英社

snippet.title: MKOI vs. BLG | CFO vs. T1 — MSI 2025 — Bracket Stage
snippet.description:
MSI 2025, LIVE FROM VANCOUVER #msi2025 

The 2025 League of Legends Mid-Season Invitational is here—bringing together the five regions to battle for glory, pride, and a critical edge heading into Worlds. As the second international showdown on the LoL Esports calendar, MSI pits two representatives from each regional league against one another in a high-stakes clash that tests their mettle at the season’s halfway mark. More than just a trophy is on the line: the winning team and the next best-performing region will earn extra slots at the World Championship, raising the stakes even higher. This year, the action unfolds beginning June 27 at the iconic Pacific Coliseum in Vancouver, Canada. Get ready for rivalries, redemption arcs, and unforgettable plays as pros will be challenged to Ignite The Fire Within.

PLAY-INS STAGE: June 27-June 29
BRACKET STAGE: July 1-July 12

You can always learn more and view the full match schedule at http://www.lolesports.com.

snippet.title: An Interstellar Object Like Oumuamua Just Enters Our Solar System: Scientists Can't Believe Its Size
snippet.description:
Astronomers have just spotted something really strange moving through our solar system — and it seems to be coming our way. This mysterious object is believed to have come from outside our solar system, making it possibly only the third known interstellar visitor ever discovered.

It’s currently being called 3I/ATLAS, and it was first seen in data collected between June 25 and June 29 by a system called ATLAS — the Asteroid Terrestrial-impact Last Alert System. This system uses powerful telescopes in Hawaii and South Africa to scan the night sky automatically for any unusual or potentially dangerous space objects.
After the object was noticed, it was confirmed by experts at NASA's Center for Near-Earth Object Studies and the International Astronomical Union's Minor Planet Center. That means it’s not just a glitch or mistake — this thing is real.

What makes 3I/ATLAS so fascinating is its strange speed and unknown nature. Scientists still aren’t sure what it actually is — it could be a comet, an asteroid, or maybe even something we’ve never seen before. One well-known astronomer, Avi Loeb from Harvard University — who famously suggested that ‘Oumuamua might have been an alien probe — has weighed in again. This time, he’s suggesting that scientists use the powerful James Webb Space Telescope to study this newly discovered interstellar object in more detail.

#interstellarobjects #oumuamua #2IBorisov #3IATLAS #interstellarvisitors #asteroid #comets #alien

id.title: Objek Antarbintang Seperti Oumuamua Baru Saja Memasuki Tata Surya Kita: Ilmuwan Tak Percaya Ukura...
id.description:
Para astronom baru saja menemukan sesuatu yang sangat aneh bergerak melalui tata surya kita — dan tampaknya benda itu akan menuju ke arah kita. Objek misterius ini diyakini berasal dari luar tata surya kita, sehingga mungkin menjadi pengunjung antarbintang ketiga yang pernah ditemukan.

Saat ini, objek tersebut disebut 3I/ATLAS, dan pertama kali terlihat dalam data yang dikumpulkan antara 25 Juni dan 29 Juni oleh sistem yang disebut ATLAS — Asteroid Terrestrial-impact Last Alert System. Sistem ini menggunakan teleskop canggih di Hawaii dan Afrika Selatan untuk memindai langit malam secara otomatis untuk mencari objek luar angkasa yang tidak biasa atau berpotensi berbahaya.

Setelah objek tersebut terlihat, hal itu dikonfirmasi oleh para ahli di Pusat Studi Objek Dekat Bumi NASA dan Pusat Planet Minor Persatuan Astronomi Internasional. Itu berarti bahwa objek ini bukan sekadar kesalahan atau kekeliruan — benda ini nyata.

Yang membuat 3I/ATLAS begitu menarik adalah kecepatannya yang aneh dan sifatnya yang tidak diketahui. Para ilmuwan masih belum yakin apa sebenarnya objek itu — bisa jadi itu adalah komet, asteroid, atau bahkan sesuatu yang belum pernah kita lihat sebelumnya. Seorang astronom terkenal, Avi Loeb dari Universitas Harvard — yang terkenal karena menyatakan bahwa ‘Oumuamua mungkin adalah wahana antariksa alien — telah memberikan tanggapan lagi. Kali ini, ia menyarankan agar para ilmuwan menggunakan Teleskop Luar Angkasa James Webb yang canggih untuk mempelajari objek antarbintang yang baru ditemukan ini secara lebih rinci.

#interstellarobjects #oumuamua #2IBorisov #3IATLAS #interstellarvisitors #asteroid #comets #alien

ja.title: オウムアムアのような恒星間物体が太陽系に突入：科学者たちはその大きさに驚いている
ja.description:
天文学者たちは、太陽系内を移動する非常に奇妙な物体を発見しました。そして、それは地球に向かって来ているようです。この謎の天体は太陽系外から来たと考えられており、おそらくこれまでに発見された3番目の恒星間訪問者となるでしょう。

この天体は「3I/ATLAS」と名付けられており、6月25日から29日にかけて「ATLAS」（小惑星地球衝突最終警報システム）と呼ばれるシステムによって収集されたデータの中で初めて確認されました。このシステムは、ハワイと南アフリカに設置された高性能望遠鏡を用いて、異常な、あるいは潜在的に危険な宇宙物体を夜空から自動的に探知します。
この天体が発見された後、NASAの地球近傍天体研究センターと国際天文学連合の小惑星センターの専門家によって確認されました。つまり、これは単なる不具合やミスではなく、実際に存在する物体なのです。

3I/ATLASの魅力は、その奇妙な速度と未知の性質にあります。科学者たちは、それが一体何なのかまだはっきりと分かっていません。彗星かもしれないし、小惑星かもしれないし、あるいは私たちがこれまで見たこともない何かかもしれないのです。ハーバード大学の著名な天文学者アヴィ・ローブ氏は、かつて「オウムアムア」が宇宙探査機だった可能性を示唆したことで有名ですが、今回再びその可能性を示唆しました。今回は、強力なジェイムズ・ウェッブ宇宙望遠鏡を用いて、この新たに発見された星間天体をより詳細に調査することを科学者に提案しています。

#interstellarobjects #oumuamua #2IBorisov #3IATLAS #interstellarvisitors #asteroid #comets #alien

pt-BR.title: Um objeto interestelar como Oumuamua acaba de entrar em nosso sistema solar: cientistas não conse...
pt-BR.description:
Astrônomos acabaram de avistar algo realmente estranho se movendo pelo nosso sistema solar — e parece estar vindo em nossa direção. Acredita-se que este objeto misterioso tenha vindo de fora do nosso sistema solar, tornando-o possivelmente o terceiro visitante interestelar já descoberto.

Atualmente, ele é chamado de 3I/ATLAS e foi visto pela primeira vez em dados coletados entre 25 e 29 de junho por um sistema chamado ATLAS — o Sistema de Último Alerta de Impacto Terrestre de Asteroide. Este sistema usa telescópios potentes no Havaí e na África do Sul para varrer o céu noturno automaticamente em busca de objetos espaciais incomuns ou potencialmente perigosos.
Depois que o objeto foi avistado, ele foi confirmado por especialistas do Centro de Estudos de Objetos Próximos à Terra da NASA e do Centro de Planetas Menores da União Astronômica Internacional. Isso significa que não é apenas uma falha ou erro — ele é real.

O que torna o 3I/ATLAS tão fascinante é sua velocidade estranha e natureza desconhecida. Os cientistas ainda não têm certeza do que realmente é — pode ser um cometa, um asteroide ou talvez até algo que nunca vimos antes. Um astrônomo renomado, Avi Loeb, da Universidade de Harvard — que sugeriu que o 'Oumuamua poderia ter sido uma sonda alienígena — voltou a se pronunciar. Desta vez, ele sugere que os cientistas usem o poderoso Telescópio Espacial James Webb para estudar este objeto interestelar recém-descoberto com mais detalhes.

#objetosinterestelares #oumuamua #2IBorisov #3IATLAS #visitantesinterestelares #asteroide #cometas #alienígena

it.title: Un oggetto interstellare simile a Oumuamua è appena entrato nel nostro sistema solare: gli scienz...
it.description:
Gli astronomi hanno appena individuato qualcosa di davvero strano muoversi nel nostro sistema solare, e sembra dirigersi verso di noi. Si ritiene che questo misterioso oggetto provenga da fuori il nostro sistema solare, il che lo rende probabilmente il terzo visitatore interstellare mai scoperto.

Attualmente si chiama 3I/ATLAS ed è stato avvistato per la prima volta nei dati raccolti tra il 25 e il 29 giugno da un sistema chiamato ATLAS, l'Asteroid Terrestrial-impact Last Alert System. Questo sistema utilizza potenti telescopi alle Hawaii e in Sudafrica per scansionare automaticamente il cielo notturno alla ricerca di oggetti spaziali insoliti o potenzialmente pericolosi.
Dopo essere stato individuato, l'oggetto è stato confermato dagli esperti del Center for Near-Earth Object Studies della NASA e del Minor Planet Center dell'Unione Astronomica Internazionale. Ciò significa che non si tratta di un semplice errore o di un problema tecnico: è reale.

Ciò che rende 3I/ATLAS così affascinante è la sua strana velocità e la sua natura sconosciuta. Gli scienziati non sono ancora certi di cosa si tratti effettivamente: potrebbe essere una cometa, un asteroide o forse persino qualcosa che non abbiamo mai visto prima. Un noto astronomo, Avi Loeb dell'Università di Harvard, che ha notoriamente ipotizzato che 'Oumuamua potesse essere una sonda aliena, è tornato a dare il suo contributo. Questa volta, suggerisce che gli scienziati utilizzino il potente telescopio spaziale James Webb per studiare più in dettaglio questo oggetto interstellare appena scoperto.

#oggettiinterstellari #oumuamua #2IBorisov #3IATLAS #visitatoriinterstellari #asteroide #comete #alieno

ko.title: 오우무아무아와 같은 성간 천체가 우리 태양계에 진입했습니다. 과학자들은 그 크기에 놀라워합니다.
ko.description:
천문학자들이 태양계를 통과하는 정말 이상한 물체를 방금 발견했습니다. 그리고 그것이 우리 쪽으로 오고 있는 것 같습니다. 이 신비로운 천체는 태양계 밖에서 온 것으로 추정되며, 아마도 지금까지 발견된 세 번째 성간 방문자일 것입니다.

이 천체는 현재 3I/ATLAS라고 불리며, ATLAS(소행성 지구 충돌 최종 경보 시스템)라는 시스템이 6월 25일부터 29일 사이에 수집한 데이터에서 처음 발견되었습니다. 이 시스템은 하와이와 남아프리카 공화국에 있는 강력한 망원경을 사용하여 밤하늘을 자동으로 스캔하여 특이하거나 잠재적으로 위험한 우주 천체를 찾아냅니다.
이 천체가 발견된 후, NASA 지구근접천체연구센터(Center for Near-Earth Object Studies)와 국제천문연맹(IAU) 소행성센터(Minor Planet Center) 전문가들이 이를 확인했습니다. 즉, 이것은 단순한 오류나 실수가 아니라 실제 존재함을 의미합니다.

3I/ATLAS를 이토록 매혹적으로 만드는 것은 그 기묘한 속도와 미지의 존재입니다. 과학자들은 아직 그것이 정확히 무엇인지 확신하지 못하고 있습니다. 혜성일 수도, 소행성일 수도, 아니면 우리가 이전에 본 적 없는 무언가일 수도 있습니다. 하버드 대학교의 저명한 천문학자 아비 로브는 오우무아무아가 외계 탐사선일 가능성을 제기했던 인물인데, 이번에 다시 한번 이 주장에 힘을 실어주었습니다. 이번에는 과학자들이 강력한 제임스 웹 우주 망원경을 사용하여 새롭게 발견된 이 성간 천체를 더 자세히 연구해야 한다고 제안했습니다.

#성간물체 #오우무아무아 #2IBorisov #3IATLAS #성간방문자 #소행성 #혜성 #외계인

fr-FR.title: Un objet interstellaire comme Oumuamua vient d'entrer dans notre système solaire : les scientifiq...
fr-FR.description:
Des astronomes viennent d'observer un objet étrange se déplaçant dans notre système solaire, et il semble se diriger vers nous. Cet objet mystérieux proviendrait de l'extérieur de notre système solaire, ce qui en fait probablement le troisième visiteur interstellaire connu jamais découvert.

Actuellement appelé 3I/ATLAS, il a été observé pour la première fois grâce à des données collectées entre le 25 et le 29 juin par un système appelé ATLAS (Asteroid Terrestrial-Impact Last Alert System). Ce système utilise de puissants télescopes situés à Hawaï et en Afrique du Sud pour scruter automatiquement le ciel nocturne à la recherche d'objets spatiaux inhabituels ou potentiellement dangereux.
Après sa détection, l'objet a été confirmé par des experts du Centre d'études des objets géocroiseurs de la NASA et du Centre des planètes mineures de l'Union astronomique internationale. Il ne s'agit donc pas d'un simple bug ou d'une erreur : il s'agit bel et bien d'un phénomène réel.

Ce qui rend 3I/ATLAS si fascinant, c'est sa vitesse étrange et sa nature inconnue. Les scientifiques ne savent toujours pas de quoi il s'agit réellement : il pourrait s'agir d'une comète, d'un astéroïde, ou peut-être même d'un objet inédit. Un astronome renommé, Avi Loeb de l'Université Harvard, qui a suggéré que ‘Oumuamua pourrait être une sonde extraterrestre, a de nouveau donné son avis. Cette fois, il suggère aux scientifiques d'utiliser le puissant télescope spatial James Webb pour étudier plus en détail cet objet interstellaire récemment découvert.

#objetsinterstellaires #oumuamua #2IBorisov #3IATLAS #visiteursinterstellaires #astéroïde #comètes #alien

de-DE.title: Ein interstellares Objekt wie Oumuamua dringt gerade in unser Sonnensystem ein: Wissenschaftler k...
de-DE.description:
Astronomen haben gerade etwas wirklich Seltsames entdeckt, das sich durch unser Sonnensystem bewegt – und es scheint auf uns zuzukommen. Dieses mysteriöse Objekt stammt vermutlich von außerhalb unseres Sonnensystems und ist möglicherweise erst der dritte bekannte interstellare Besucher, der jemals entdeckt wurde.

Es trägt derzeit die Bezeichnung 3I/ATLAS und wurde erstmals in Daten beobachtet, die zwischen dem 25. und 29. Juni von einem System namens ATLAS – dem Asteroid Terrestrial-impact Last Alert System – gesammelt wurden. Dieses System nutzt leistungsstarke Teleskope auf Hawaii und Südafrika, um den Nachthimmel automatisch nach ungewöhnlichen oder potenziell gefährlichen Weltraumobjekten abzusuchen.
Nachdem das Objekt entdeckt worden war, wurde es von Experten des Center for Near-Earth Object Studies der NASA und des Minor Planet Center der Internationalen Astronomischen Union bestätigt. Das bedeutet, dass es sich nicht nur um eine Störung oder einen Fehler handelt – das Ding ist real.

Was 3I/ATLAS so faszinierend macht, ist seine ungewöhnliche Geschwindigkeit und seine unbekannte Natur. Wissenschaftler sind sich noch immer nicht sicher, was es genau ist – es könnte ein Komet, ein Asteroid oder vielleicht sogar etwas völlig Neues sein. Avi Loeb, ein bekannter Astronom von der Harvard University, der bekanntlich vermutete, dass es sich bei ʻOumuamua um eine außerirdische Sonde gehandelt haben könnte, meldet sich erneut zu Wort. Dieses Mal schlägt er vor, das leistungsstarke James-Webb-Weltraumteleskop zu nutzen, um dieses neu entdeckte interstellare Objekt genauer zu untersuchen.

nl-NL.title: Een interstellair object zoals Oumuamua is zojuist ons zonnestelsel binnengekomen: wetenschappers...
nl-NL.description:
Astronomen hebben zojuist iets heel vreemds door ons zonnestelsel zien bewegen – en het lijkt onze kant op te komen. Men vermoedt dat dit mysterieuze object van buiten ons zonnestelsel komt, wat het mogelijk pas de derde interstellaire bezoeker maakt die ooit is ontdekt.

Het wordt momenteel 3I/ATLAS genoemd en werd voor het eerst gezien in gegevens die tussen 25 en 29 juni werden verzameld door een systeem genaamd ATLAS – het Asteroid Terrestrial-impact Last Alert System. Dit systeem gebruikt krachtige telescopen op Hawaï en Zuid-Afrika om de nachtelijke hemel automatisch af te speuren naar ongewone of potentieel gevaarlijke ruimteobjecten.
Nadat het object was opgemerkt, werd het bevestigd door experts van NASA's Center for Near-Earth Object Studies en het Minor Planet Center van de Internationale Astronomische Unie. Dat betekent dat het niet zomaar een storing of vergissing is – dit is echt.

Wat 3I/ATLAS zo fascinerend maakt, is de vreemde snelheid en onbekende aard ervan. Wetenschappers weten nog steeds niet wat het precies is – het zou een komeet, een asteroïde of misschien zelfs iets wat we nog nooit eerder hebben gezien kunnen zijn. Een bekende astronoom, Avi Loeb van Harvard University – die beroemd werd door zijn suggestie dat ‘Oumuamua mogelijk een buitenaardse sonde was – heeft zich opnieuw uitgesproken. Dit keer stelt hij voor dat wetenschappers de krachtige James Webb-ruimtetelescoop gebruiken om dit nieuw ontdekte interstellaire object gedetailleerder te bestuderen.

pl.title: Międzygwiezdny obiekt taki jak Oumuamua właśnie wleciał do naszego Układu Słonecznego: Naukowcy n...
pl.description:
Astronomowie właśnie zauważyli coś naprawdę dziwnego poruszającego się w naszym układzie słonecznym — i wydaje się, że zmierza w naszą stronę. Uważa się, że ten tajemniczy obiekt przybył spoza naszego układu słonecznego, co czyni go prawdopodobnie zaledwie trzecim znanym międzygwiezdnym gościem, jakiego kiedykolwiek odkryto.

Obecnie nosi nazwę 3I/ATLAS i został po raz pierwszy zauważony w danych zebranych między 25 a 29 czerwca przez system o nazwie ATLAS — Asteroid Terrestrial-impact Last Alert System. System ten wykorzystuje potężne teleskopy na Hawajach i w Republice Południowej Afryki do automatycznego skanowania nocnego nieba w poszukiwaniu nietypowych lub potencjalnie niebezpiecznych obiektów kosmicznych.
Po zauważeniu obiektu eksperci z Centrum Badań Obiektów Bliskich Ziemi NASA i Centrum Małych Planet Międzynarodowej Unii Astronomicznej potwierdzili jego obecność. Oznacza to, że nie jest to tylko usterka lub pomyłka — ta rzecz jest prawdziwa.

To, co sprawia, że ​​3I/ATLAS jest tak fascynujący, to jego dziwna prędkość i nieznana natura. Naukowcy wciąż nie są pewni, czym to właściwie jest — może to być kometa, asteroida, a może nawet coś, czego nigdy wcześniej nie widzieliśmy. Jeden znany astronom, Avi Loeb z Uniwersytetu Harvarda — który słynnie zasugerował, że ‘Oumuamua mogła być sondą kosmiczną — ponownie zabrał głos. Tym razem sugeruje, aby naukowcy wykorzystali potężny Teleskop Kosmiczny Jamesa Webba do dokładniejszego zbadania tego nowo odkrytego obiektu międzygwiezdnego.

#interstellarobjects #oumuamua #2IBorisov #3IATLAS #interstellarvisitors #asteroid #comets #alien

es-US.title: Un objeto interestelar como Oumuamua acaba de entrar en nuestro sistema solar: los científicos no...
es-US.description:
Los astrónomos acaban de avistar algo realmente extraño moviéndose por nuestro sistema solar, y parece que se dirige hacia nosotros. Se cree que este misterioso objeto proviene de fuera de nuestro sistema solar, lo que lo convierte posiblemente en el tercer visitante interestelar conocido jamás descubierto.

Actualmente se le conoce como 3I/ATLAS y fue visto por primera vez en datos recopilados entre el 25 y el 29 de junio por un sistema llamado ATLAS (Sistema de Última Alerta de Impacto Terrestre de Asteroides). Este sistema utiliza potentes telescopios en Hawái y Sudáfrica para escanear el cielo nocturno automáticamente en busca de objetos espaciales inusuales o potencialmente peligrosos.
Tras la detección del objeto, fue confirmado por expertos del Centro de Estudios de Objetos Cercanos a la Tierra de la NASA y del Centro de Planetas Menores de la Unión Astronómica Internacional. Esto significa que no se trata de un simple fallo técnico ni de un error: es real.

Lo que hace a 3I/ATLAS tan fascinante es su extraña velocidad y su naturaleza desconocida. Los científicos aún no están seguros de qué es realmente: podría ser un cometa, un asteroide o incluso algo nunca antes visto. Un conocido astrónomo, Avi Loeb, de la Universidad de Harvard, quien famosamente sugirió que ‘Oumuamua podría haber sido una sonda extraterrestre, ha vuelto a opinar. En esta ocasión, sugiere que los científicos utilicen el potente Telescopio Espacial James Webb para estudiar con más detalle este objeto interestelar recién descubierto.

hi.title: ओउमुआमुआ जैसी एक अंतरतारकीय वस्तु हमारे सौरमंडल में प्रवेश कर गई है: वैज्ञानिक इसके आकार पर विश्व...
hi.description:
खगोलविदों ने अभी-अभी हमारे सौर मंडल में घूमते हुए कुछ बहुत ही अजीबोगरीब वस्तु देखी है - और ऐसा लगता है कि यह हमारी ओर आ रही है। माना जाता है कि यह रहस्यमयी वस्तु हमारे सौर मंडल के बाहर से आई है, जिससे यह संभवतः अब तक खोजी गई तीसरी ज्ञात अंतरतारकीय वस्तु बन गई है।

इसे वर्तमान में 3I/ATLAS कहा जा रहा है, और इसे पहली बार 25 जून से 29 जून के बीच ATLAS नामक एक प्रणाली द्वारा एकत्र किए गए डेटा में देखा गया था - क्षुद्रग्रह स्थलीय-प्रभाव अंतिम चेतावनी प्रणाली। यह प्रणाली हवाई और दक्षिण अफ्रीका में शक्तिशाली दूरबीनों का उपयोग करके रात के आकाश को किसी भी असामान्य या संभावित खतरनाक अंतरिक्ष वस्तु के लिए स्वचालित रूप से स्कैन करती है।

इस वस्तु के देखे जाने के बाद, नासा के सेंटर फॉर नियर-अर्थ ऑब्जेक्ट स्टडीज और इंटरनेशनल एस्ट्रोनॉमिकल यूनियन के माइनर प्लेनेट सेंटर के विशेषज्ञों द्वारा इसकी पुष्टि की गई। इसका मतलब है कि यह केवल एक गड़बड़ी या गलती नहीं है - यह चीज़ वास्तविक है।

3I/ATLAS को इतना आकर्षक बनाने वाली बात इसकी अजीब गति और अज्ञात प्रकृति है। वैज्ञानिकों को अभी भी यकीन नहीं है कि यह वास्तव में क्या है - यह एक धूमकेतु, एक क्षुद्रग्रह या शायद कुछ ऐसा भी हो सकता है जिसे हमने पहले कभी नहीं देखा है। हार्वर्ड विश्वविद्यालय के एक प्रसिद्ध खगोलशास्त्री एवी लोएब - जिन्होंने प्रसिद्ध रूप से सुझाव दिया था कि 'ओउमुआमुआ एक एलियन जांच हो सकती है - ने फिर से अपना विचार व्यक्त किया है। इस बार, वह सुझाव दे रहे हैं कि वैज्ञानिक इस नई खोजी गई अंतरतारकीय वस्तु का अधिक विस्तार से अध्ययन करने के लिए शक्तिशाली जेम्स वेब स्पेस टेलीस्कोप का उपयोग करें।

snippet.title: Taking My Next Step.
snippet.description:
Bâan -The Boundary of Adulthood - 
A story of two people in search of a new life, who leave their birthplaces - traveling to a whole different world trying to find a place where they truly belong. Set in the fictional world of Euthania, a land rich in nature with various magical races based on South East Asian Mythology, which is connected to Japan via a warp gate.

snippet.title: Wait...The Worst Possible US Disaster Just Got EVEN WORSE?!? (Cascadia Megaquake)
snippet.description:
The Big One is coming and it could be far worse than anyone imagined.

The Cascadia Subduction Zone, just off the Pacific Northwest coast, is building toward a massive earthquake and tsunami. But new research reveals an even more terrifying possibility: widespread toxic spills, infrastructure collapse, wildfires, and deadly gas plumes. All triggered by a single seismic event.

In this episode of Weathered, we dig into the science behind the Cascadia Megaquake, why the Pacific Northwest is especially vulnerable, and how climate change could make it worse. We explore what you can do to stay safe and why your community might be your best line of defense.
